title: Congratulations, You Shared Yourself...
itunes:title: Congratulations, You Shared Yourself...
description:
MON 10/24 - Big shout out to DJ Khaled and his fiance Nicole Tuck on the birth of their baby boy. The Snapchat King even shared the birth on social media and people are wondering, "Is that oversharing? Or is that the new norm?" Then we address the birthday boy Drake going in on Kid Cudi in his new song "Two Birds One Stone". Did he go too far by putting Cudi's addiction problems in his bars? Are we just doin' too much nowadays???
